jobs.prompt:
Run the Guba rumor monitor to track retail sentiment for portfolio A-shares.

STEP 1: Run `python3 ~/.hermes/scripts/guba_rumor_monitor.py` to get attention index data.

STEP 2: For any stocks with 关注指数 > 85 AND positive rank change (排名变化 > 0), scrape their 股吧 hot posts:
- Navigate to `https://guba.eastmoney.com/list,{STOCK_CODE},99.html`
- Wait 3 seconds for page load
- Use browser_console to extract posts:
  ```javascript
  (() => {
    const rows = document.querySelectorAll('table tbody tr');
    const posts = [];
    rows.forEach(row => {
      const cells = row.querySelectorAll('td');
      if (cells.length >= 5) {
        const titleEl = cells[2]?.querySelector('a');
        if (titleEl && titleEl.textContent.trim().length > 5) {
          posts.push({
            reads: parseInt(cells[0]?.textContent?.trim() || '0'),
            comments: parseInt(cells[1]?.textContent?.trim() || '0'),
            title: titleEl.textContent.trim(),
            author: cells[3]?.textContent?.trim() || '',
            time: cells[4]?.textContent?.trim() || ''
          });
        }
      }
    });
    return JSON.stringify(posts.slice(0, 5));
  })()
  ```
- Score each post for rumor keywords (传闻, 据传, 未证实, 爆料, 内部消息, 据说, 网传, 独家, 突发, 重磅, 超预期, 大订单, 重大合同, 收购, 重组, 技术突破, 2.4T, 800G, 1.6T)
- If any post has reads > 500 or comments > 10 AND contains a rumor keyword, include it in the alert

STEP 3: Output alerts in this format:
- 📈 关注指数飙升: Stock, attention change, rank change, price
- 🔥 高关注度 + 📌 热门传闻: Stock, attention, top rumor post title, engagement metrics

Only output if there are alerts. Stay silent if no significant activity.
